mock.onGet("/api/data-list/products").reply(function () {
  return [200, JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(data.products)).reverse()];
}); // POST : Add new Item

mock.onPost("/api/data-list/products/").reply(function (request) {
  // Get event from post data
  var item = JSON.parse(request.data).item;
  var length = data.products.length;
  var lastIndex = 0;

  if (length) {
    lastIndex = data.products[length - 1].id;
  }

  item.id = lastIndex + 1;
  data.products.push(item);
  return [201, {
    id: item.id
  }];
}); // Update Product

mock.onPost(/\/api\/data-list\/products\/\d+/).reply(function (request) {
  var itemId = request.url.substring(request.url.lastIndexOf("/") + 1);
  var item = data.products.find(function (item) {
    return item.id == itemId;
  });
  Object.assign(item, JSON.parse(request.data).item);
  return [200, item];
}); // DELETE: Remove Item

mock.onDelete(/\/api\/data-list\/products\/\d+/).reply(function (request) {
  var itemId = request.url.substring(request.url.lastIndexOf("/") + 1);
  var itemIndex = data.products.findIndex(function (p) {
    return p.id == itemId;
  });
  data.products.splice(itemIndex, 1);
  return [200];
});
